April 5th: You asked and we listened! Building on the success of the Personal® App for iPhone®  we are proud to.announce that the T. Rowe Price Personal® App for iPad® is now available in the App Store™.. Bug fixes  along with enhanced functionality and reporting of performance to better monitor and improve your.experience.

We apologize for any.inconvenience.. • Multi leg option trading.• Option chain enhancements.• Trade specific shares for stocks/ETFs.• Tax.lots for your positions.• Margin trades in your IRA.• Extended hours trading.• Improved balance.displays.• Easily accessible quote lookup. The time has come! With Fidelity Mobile for Apple Watch  find out what’s moving the markets with a twist of your.wrist. See a markets Glance view  push alerts  real time access to domestic and international markets  market movers .and recent quotes.

This May  change isn’t in the air; it’s at your fingertips. That’s because we’ve added an additional touch of.security with Touch ID  along with a handful of other updates.. Enjoy quicker access with Touch ID  available for supported devices with iOS 8.. View extended hours chart data for securities that trade on the pre/post market. . Price Improvement information now displayed for your orders. See how Fidelity helps identify and qualify your orders.executed outside the National Best Bid or Offer (NBBO).
This summer  we’ve turned up the heat and optimized our resolution.. Optimized for iPhone 6 and 6 Plus.. Notification badge is now cleared after tapping the app icon.

Quotes have been updated with a new layout to optimize the display of information. Now research content is.available as part of the Stock Quote  and work is underway for additional security types..Place a trade or get a.quote quickly and conveniently from your price trigger notifications on your iPhone  iPad  or Apple Watch™..Access.market information  Watch Lists and recent quotes with your Today Widget by swiping down from the top of the screen .tapping on the Today tab and adding the Fidelity widget in the edit section at the bottom of the feed.

Account Open: Easily open select Fidelity accounts in the mobile app. Accounts include Brokerage  Cash Management .Rollover IRA  Traditional IRA  and Roth IRA. Fund your new account in a number of ways  including mobile check.deposit.. Charts are now available on your Apple Watch™ for Stock  ETF  and Index quotes. Swipe the chart to change from a.1 Day to a 30 Day display.. Support for iOS 9
We’ve improved the Fidelity Mobile® Check Deposit experience with enhanced camera technology for taking quick .clear images.

Quick Access: View your Balances  Watch Lists  and Real Time Quotes without having to log in. . Notebook: Capture ideas about your current holdings or potential investments with the new Notebook from Fidelity..Access the full Notebook from our main menu or view and add a note about a security from the Quote screen. Quickly see.which securities you’ve created notes for from the Positions and Watch Lists screens. Save articles to your Notebook.with the new Share Extension in your mobile browser.

We improved the Notebook  allowing you to add a photo from your camera roll. Snap a photo of an investment idea .and never lose sight of an opportunity again. . Video content upgraded to live streaming Bloomberg TV.. Supports iOS 8  9
We’ve expanded our quote screen to include the same mutual fund research you have access to on Fidelity.com. Now.see additional details on fund performance  ratings  composition  and more. .

We’ve made our biggest update yet!.• New and improved design and navigation.• Introducing the Feed  with.information tailored to your investments and interests (with regular updates on the way).• Updated Accounts section.with summary information and a consolidated activity tab.• Reimagined Watch Lists and research experience.•.Additional News   Video sources  including Fidelity Viewpoints.• Accessibility enhancements and more!

We are constantly looking for ways to improve the app based on your feedback. Look for: .• Continued updates.to Feed.• Account and Watch List enhancements to view more detail on your screen.• Defect fixes

Bug fixes:.1. Payment amount display is now limited to 2 fractional digits. In version 3.0.1 certain payment.amounts were being displayed with an excessive amount of digits  which could impede the payment workflow. .2. The.currency symbol for payment amounts is now always the dollar symbol. In versions 3.0.0 and 3.0.1  currency symbols were.based on iOS's user modifiable Region setting. This could result in end user confusion. Reflecting non US Region.settings is not appropriate when making payments on bills denominated in U.S dollars.

We’re proud and excited to release FlightAware v5.0 — a MAJOR update for iOS 9 with an all new and improved look.and feel  plus lots of additional features for a better user experience!.   Recent searches and alerts are displayed on the landing view..  Omnisearch allows you to simultaneously search.for flights  tail numbers  airports  and cities..  Nearby flights can be displayed in a list and sorted by various.data points..  Quickly filter search results using just about any data point: airline  flight status  origin .destination  etc..  When searching by tail number you can now view aircraft registration details and photos from.the flight detail section..  Local search history is now synced with web search history..  Improved support.for Voiceover accessibility.
This maintenance update includes fixes for several of the bugs encountered with the initial release. .

Unit Conversion.   Choose between Fahrenheit and Celsius.   Choose between US Customary and Metric.    Airline lookup is now supported when searching by flight.   Search functionality has.been streamlined to allow for searching without first selecting an Omnisearch result .   When searching by route.you can now exchange origin and destination and perform a new search directly from the results page.   Support for.searching by route and tail number has been added to the alert creation workflow. UI Enhancements.   Pull to refresh has been added to the airport view.   Support for viewing map fullscreen.on landing  flight  and airport views.   Map centering and panning behavior as been improved to account for.fullscreen mode. Other Updates.   More consistent display of flight and weather data with appropriate units .   Airport view.displays delay information on main screen.   Additional flight information provided on flight detail view.  .Sign In/Sign Out has been added to the settings view.   Several bug fixes and UI tweaks

Thank you for using FlightAware! We've made a bunch of improvements based on your feedback!. Release 5.2 includes the following:. * The search workflow has been updated to better handle slower network connections..* The landing page has been.updated to better integrate search history with the search bar and to display cached searches and notifications while.retrieving updated information in the background..* iPhones can be placed in landscape orientation to display the.map without a user interface..* A “Where's my plane?" button will display on the flight detail landing screen if.the flight has been delayed or has not yet departed..* Airport names have been added to the flight details view..* We updated terminology to use the word “Notifications” instead of “Alerts.” . * The dark theme UI background.color has been altered to increase readability across all map tile types..* The notification creation workflow has.been updated with minor improvements to help with the creation and editing of notifications..* Additional bug fixes.and internal changes.. Please email supportflightaware.com to leave feedback and suggestions  since we are unable to reply to reviews..Don't forget to rate us 5 stars in iTunes if you love our app. We really appreciate it!

10% OFF WAHOO FITNESS PRODUCTS   To celebrate our new support of ANT   Wahoo Fitness is offering 10% off of all of.their products until October 31  2011. To receive the discount  visit abvio.com/wahoo and enter code ABV1031 during.checkout. . Walkmeter 6.0 continues a track record of innovation  ease of use  and power. . INTERVAL TRAINING.Interval training allows any kind of interval workout to be easily created and used  from.simple repeated intervals to a complete pyramid interval plan. Intervals can be based on time  distance  reaching a.specific location  or advanced using the lap button. Using text to speech technology  voice prompts for each interval.can be customized to any specific command. Summary statistics for intervals are shown on the iPhone  within Google Maps .and can be exported for further analysis. . ANT  SUPPORT FOR HEART RATE MONITORS  BIKE SPEED  AND BIKE CADENCE.6.0 adds support for the Wahoo Fitness ANT .system (purchased separately)  allowing heart rate monitors and speed/cadence cycling sensors to be employed for.performance measurement and feedback. Unlike other apps that only record sensor data for later analysis  our app.provides a deep implementation and real time feedback. For example  calories are calculated using heart rate and VO2Max.data. Cycling distance  speed  and stop detection are calculated using sensor data. Target announcements can be set.based on this information. . TARGET ANNOUNCEMENTS.Target announcements can be set for heart rate  speed  pace  or cycling cadence  providing.real time feedback. Targets can be set per activity or per interval. When you are outside your target range  an.announcement gives you feedback  such as "Increase Speed" or "Decrease Heart Rate"  along with your current stats..Targets can be set for the whole workout or to individual intervals. . ZONES.Zones allows for easy selection of target announcement ranges  but more importantly  allows post workout.analysis of performance. Every workout can be analyzed using zones for heart rate  speed  pace  and cycling cadence. For.example  you could see how much time  how much distance  and how many calories were spent while pace is in a certain.range. Zones are configurable to any ranges  and can be applied to any workout  both during and after a workout. . LAP BUTTON.Tap the lap button at any point during a workout to record all of the data up to that point as an.interval  and summarize a dozen different statistics such as time and distance covered  average pace  fastest pace  and.maximum heart rate. . AND MORE.➤ Split distance may be configured per activity. .➤ Splits/Intervals/Zones may be viewed via a.button on the stopwatch. .➤ Easily enable and disable email updates  Twitter  Facebook  and dailymile via a button.on the stopwatch. .➤ Dozens more statistics can be viewed in the stopwatch  announced  and listed in Facebook .Twitter  and dailymile. Includes splits and interval statistics. .➤ All graphs may now be viewed over time or.distance. Added graphs for heart rate and bike cadence. .➤ Calendar summaries may be exported to CSV. .➤ An.import URL can be entered in advanced settings for when iOS does not automatically launch our app to handle an import...➤ Activities may be set to summarize into other activities  and then viewed using the Summary button in the.Calendar view. . Updated for iOS 7!   Walkmeter is updated for iOS 7 with a beautiful design that supports iOS 7 principles:. Clarity   Walkmeter was redesigned with a clarity as a primary goal. Fonts are bigger  and have more contrast. Simple.words replace embossed buttons. Icons are simpler and brighter. Distance markers are crisp and more readable. These and.more lead to a beautiful and functional design that is a joy to use. . Deference   The design of Walkmeter defers to your workout data. The Stopwatch is now full width  making your stats.top priority. Stopwatch stats is not unobscured by buttons  nor surrounded by chrome. Graphs are high contrast  with.appropriate use of color. The Stopwatch can have a black or white background  based on your viewing preference..Deference allows you to pay attention to what is most important. . Depth   Depth is used to give context of where you are and what you are doing. Views brought up over the map and.other content are now translucent  giving context to your interactions. History navigation allows you to easily drill.down by workout  activity  day  month  and year. . We have also preserved the core values that have made Walkmeter among the most highly rated GPS fitness apps in the.world: Innovative capabilities that exceed any other application today. An iPhone centric design that is reliable and.keeps you in control of your data. And customer service that is dedicated to your satisfaction. . We hope you like our new design  and we look forward to helping you meet your fitness goals. . Other notes: .• Updated History view to show summaries by activity  year  month  week and day. Moved summaries.for activities  routes  bikes  shoes  and competitors to their own tab views. .• Also supports iOS 6 and 5 using.our previous user interface.

Thanks so much for your feedback and support!.        These and more.lead to design that has increased emphasis on function.. 10% OFF WAHOO FITNESS PRODUCTS   To celebrate our new support of ANT   Wahoo Fitness is offering 10% off of all of.their products until October 31  2011. To receive the discount  visit abvio.com/wahoo and enter code ABV1031 during.checkout. . Cyclemeter 6.0 continues a track record of innovation  ease of use  and power. . INTERVAL TRAINING.Interval training allows any kind of interval workout to be easily created and used  from.simple repeated intervals to a complete pyramid interval plan. Intervals can be based on time  distance  reaching a.specific location  or advanced using the lap button. Using text to speech technology  voice prompts for each interval.can be customized to any specific command. Summary statistics for intervals are shown on the iPhone  within Google Maps .and can be exported for further analysis. . ANT  SUPPORT FOR HEART RATE MONITORS  BIKE SPEED  AND BIKE CADENCE.6.0 adds support for the Wahoo Fitness ANT .system (purchased separately)  allowing heart rate monitors and speed/cadence cycling sensors to be employed for.performance measurement and feedback. Unlike other apps that only record sensor data for later analysis  our app.provides a deep implementation and real time feedback. For example  calories are calculated using heart rate and VO2Max.data. Cycling distance  speed  and stop detection are calculated using sensor data. Target announcements can be set.based on this information. . TARGET ANNOUNCEMENTS.Target announcements can be set for heart rate  speed  pace  or cycling cadence  providing.real time feedback. Targets can be set per activity or per interval. When you are outside your target range  an.announcement gives you feedback  such as "Increase Speed" or "Decrease Heart Rate"  along with your current stats..Targets can be set for the whole workout or to individual intervals. . ZONES.Zones allows for easy selection of target announcement ranges  but more importantly  allows post workout.analysis of performance. Every workout can be analyzed using zones for heart rate  speed  pace  and cycling cadence. For.example  you could see how much time  how much distance  and how many calories were spent while pace is in a certain.range. Zones are configurable to any ranges  and can be applied to any workout  both during and after a workout. . LAP BUTTON.Tap the lap button at any point during a workout to record all of the data up to that point as an.interval  and summarize a dozen different statistics such as time and distance covered  average pace  fastest pace  and.maximum heart rate. . Updated for iOS 7!   Cyclemeter is updated for iOS 7 with a beautiful design that supports iOS 7 principles:. Clarity   Cyclemeter was redesigned with clarity as a primary goal. Distance markers are crisp and readable. Fonts.are bigger  and have more contrast. Simple words replace embossed buttons. Icons are simpler and brighter. These and.more lead to design that has increased emphasis on function.. Deference   The design of Cyclemeter defers to your workout data. The Stopwatch is now full width  making your stats.top priority. Stopwatch stats are not obscured by buttons  nor surrounded by chrome. Graphs are high contrast  with.appropriate use of color. The Stopwatch can have a black or white background  based on your viewing preference..Deference allows you to pay attention to what is most important. . Depth   Depth is used to give context of where you are and what you are doing. Views brought up over the map and.other content are now translucent  giving context to your interactions. History navigation allows you to easily drill.down by workout  activity  day  month  and year. . We have also preserved the core values that have made Cyclemeter among the most highly rated GPS fitness apps in the.world: Innovative capabilities that exceed any other application today. An iPhone centric design that is reliable and.keeps you in control of your data. And customer service that is dedicated to your satisfaction. . We hope you like our new design. We look forward to helping you meet your fitness goals. . Other notes: .• Updated History view to show summaries by activity  year  month  week and day. Moved summaries.for activities  routes  bikes  shoes  and competitors to their own tab views. .• Also supports iOS 6 and 5 using.our previous user interface.

• Pumped up colors to be more readable in sunlight. .• Increased font weight used for statistics (configurable.in Stopwatch settings). .• Switched the default stopwatch background to black. .• Fixed display of Facebook .Twitter  dailymile  and Email Update posts. .• Fixed Facebook repeated stories.  . We are pleased to announce that all National Geographic map layers have been edited and updated to reflect the.latest information from our 10th Edition Atlas of the World. . Please note that if you downloaded maps for offline use in the past  you will need to download the new map layers.again in order to see the updated layers. . As always  we value your feedback.

National Geographic’s World Atlas has been completely rebuilt and redesigned. We've given the app a new look  a.sleek new interface  and a host of new features—including daily trivia  an innovative statistics visualizer  and a much.improved measuring tool. . You still have all the same functionality and features you’ve come to expect from the Atlas  but we’ve listened to.your comments and suggestions and made it easier to use  more stable  and more elegant. . MAJOR CHANGES.   All maps and location information have been updated.  Bing maps have been removed  which means no more jarring.style change when zooming beyond Nat Geo cartography.  The distance measuring tool is now much more functional.  Offline map downloads have been decreased from ~500MB in size to 125MB in size  meaning they download fast and don’t.take up as much space on your device.  You now have the ability to sync your saved pins across your devices

We appreciate all of the constructive feedback we've received since launching our completely redesigned World.Atlas app. We've listened to your feedback and have made several enhancements. .   The app should feel more responsive in general. .  We’ve reduced a lag in performance on some older devices .and relaxed the animations between sections to allow you to interact directly. .  Fixed some odd scenarios that.could occur when activating the app from a notification. .  Fixed a rare crash event that could occur with the star.field.  Fixed a rare crash event that could cause certain saved pins to crash the app. .  Pins: We are.investigating the issues reported with older pin lists. But  you will now be able to access your "imported" pins.faster  as it now appears first in the "Saved Pins" list. . In case you missed it   here’s what was new in version 4.0: .   .  .

Home View “Zoom In” support includes the ability to zoom in and out via pinch gestures or double tapping  making.it easier to view details for devices in specific areas of the home..   Modes feature allows the user to control a multitude of lifestyle devices in the home with the click of a single.button. For example  click on the Mode button and select  “Out for the Day” to turn off specific lights  lock the doors.and raise the temperature. This can be set up through the ADT PulseSM web portal by going to Automations/Add.Automation/Trigger: When Mode Starts. From there  multiple actions can be tied to a Mode..   Multi Action Automations allow the user to set up multiple automations at the same time instead of one by one..Automations can also be set to begin on a delay of up to 30 minutes  which may be based on a single trigger. For.example  if the front door is opened  the automation could turn on all the lights  wait 15 seconds  unlock all the doors.and then lower the temperature. Use the Automations/Add Automations feature on the ADT Pulse web portal and select a.trigger. Once a trigger is selected  multiple automations can be added. .

Unfortunately  the update we pushed out.on Monday in spite of having very  very minimal changes related specifically to iOS8 managed to drag in with it some.unexpected new issues related to jumping from the original code (built on iOS5 and 6) to iOS8. Those issues tended to.manifest themselves in part based on specific user data and scenarios we didn't catch or were unable to catch in.testing.. We have since expanded our beta test group and put this version through more rigorous testing to ensure the bugs.reported on 2.6 are now fixed.. :). CRITICAL UPDATE–PLEAES READ! THIS UPDATE FIXES THE PROBLEM WITH WEB SEARCHES not brining up any results. Please.read this to learn how the new version works. . WHAT HAPPENED? WHY DID THE APP STOP WORKING? Our app used Google's free Image Search feature for the web library.searches. 3rd party apps use what is called an "API" to communicate with the Google image feature. On December 1st .Google deprecated (discontinued support for) their free image search API and turned it off breaking our app's web.searches causing any web image searches to stop working. . HOW DID YOU FIX IT? Google has replaced their free API with a paid version. However using Google's new paid API.was not an option for us as it would cost way more than what we charge for the app so that was not feasible. So What.we did was to actually embed the Google Image search web page right into the app. This restores the complete web search.functionality to the app but behaves a little differently. Please keep reading to understand how the new system.works:. The Web Library tab has been renamed the Web Search tab and the My Library tab has been renamed to Favorites.. You perform web searches just as before by either selecting one of the "featured" searches (i.e. Happy Birthday .Good Morning I Miss You etc.) or entering in what you're looking for (i.e. red corvette funny baby etc.).. Now however instead of the results showing up in the normal thumbnail view like it was before (and how it still.works on the Library tab) it will actually show you the search results in a Google web page. Scroll down to see the.thumbnails which look better in many ways as they keep the aspect ratio of the image and show them larger. When you.find one you like tap on it and swipe right and left as usual. HOWEVER and this is the important part to use one of.the images (to customize share crop etc. ) you HOLD YOUR FINGER DOWN ON THE IMAGE FOR A SECOND and it will pull that.image into the app so you can customize it share it save it etc.. IMPORTANT! If you hold your finger down on one of the thumbnails it will only bring in a low resolution version.of the image and any animations will not play so be sure and tap on the thumbnail first so it enlarges to full.resolution and then hold your finger on that image to pull it into the app. (NOTE: It may take a second or two for.the full resolution version of the image to download and you can't pull the image into the app until it has so if you.hold your finger down for a second or two and it doesn't pull in it is likely still getting the high res version so.just lift your finger and try again.). Here is a video that shows how this works if you need help with this: http://tinyurl.com/clipishwebsearch. Sorry for any inconvenience to you that was caused by Google discontinuing their free image API but we hope you'll.continue to enjoy the app as always with the changes we've made. Thanks!

Hello!. Genius Scan 3.1 is a major update which considerably speeds up your workflow! With this update  we focused on making.exporting documents even more convenient.. ✔ Multiple default email addresses.You can now enter several default email addresses in the settings by just.separating them with a semi colon. Default email addresses are very convenient when you always have to send your.receipts or documents to the same email address.. ✔ Improved help system. If you have a question  you are likely to find an answer in the Help menu of the.app.. ✔ Ability to customize the email signature (Genius Scan ).You can now customize the signature in the emails sent.from Genius Scan. . ✔ Export to Microsoft SkyDrive. Microsoft SkyDrive is a cloud file storage system. Genius Scan  now lets you.upload your scans directly to SkyDrive.. ✔ Extended Expensify support. Expensify lets you create better expense reports. Previously in Genius Scan   you.could scan your receipts and send them to Expensify. You can now add the useful transaction details: date  comment .merchant  amount  currency.. ✔ Support folder for Google Drive. You can now choose which folder you would like to upload your scans to.. ✔ Export plugins remember the folder you have previously chosen. When you export to a cloud service like.Dropbox  you often want to use the same directory several times in a row. But you don’t want to choose it again and.again. Genius Scan  helps you now by remembering which one you used the previous time.. ✔ Support changing the file title with Dropbox. When exporting a scan to Dropbox  you can now change the.filename.. ✔ Support OCR with Google Drive. Google Drive offers to OCR documents when they are uploaded. We have added a.switch to let you turn it on.. We also fixed a few annoyances:.✔ Fixed issue with Dropbox login.✔ Solved multiple bugs with Box.✔.Fixed bug ignoring the Evernote notebook the user was choosing.

Bonjour ! . Genius Scan 3.8 brings you all the tools to safely store your documents and export them to new destinations.. TOUCH ID.You can now protect Genius Scan with Touch ID. When enabled  you won’t be able to enter Genius Scan.without identifying yourself with your fingerprint. If you forgot your fingerprints – or if your phone doesn’t have.Touch ID – you can always use a good old passcode.. PDF ENCRYPTION.You may want to transmit PDF documents securely so that they can’t be read from anyone but the.recipient. By setting a password on your PDF document  you can ensure that the NSA won’t snoop on them (well… we can’t.really promise that but it should keep most people out).. SUGARSYNC.SugarSync is a popular document storage service with tons of powerful features. A popular request.among our users was to support it. Today is the day.. MULTISELECT.The last version of Genius Scan brought you numerous features with the new multi selection  enabling.batch export  merging  deleting. We have tweaked and improved the amazing multi select features from Genius Scan 3.7... and … BUG FIXES.  Seconds are back in the document name when exporting a scan directly to avoid name collisions.since you’re fast enough to scan two documents in the same minute!.  Fixes issues when importing PDF files from the.cloud. WHAT’S NEXT?.Genius Scan 4.0.
Fix compatibility issues with iOS 8.3.  Fix issues with Uploads view.

Hi all! . First thanks to everyone for all of your feedback and comments. We have been working hard to fix bugs and your.feedback has been extremely helpful to us. Please continue to leave reviews we are reading them!. Second we started an FAQ for our app here: https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Apps/FAQ. Check it.out if you have questions.. Third as you may of noticed we are also releasing more frequent updates. We want to make sure we get fixes out to.everyone as fast as possible. Reading your reviews doesn’t do us much good if we don’t ship our fixes!. Whew! With that out of the way here is what’s in the latest release. (Hint: Bug fixes!). * Faster page rendering! . * Re added a ”delete all" button saved pages. * New buttons to see "similar pages" and "page issues" in an article. * Fix to properly display Latin titles. I’m looking at you Lichtheimia corymbifera!. * Added more informative descriptions to the saved pages list. * New translations Thanks to everyone who contributed we are truly grateful! This app wouldn’t be possible without.your contributions. (If you would like to help translate our app please check out this link to find out more: https://translatewiki.net/wiki/Translating:WikimediaMobile). * Many fixes to make info boxes and tables work more reliably. * Various fixes to improve overall article viewing and loading. * Fix for images not displaying properly in lists. * Fix for a crash when viewing an image gallery. * Several fixes for crashes that occur during data migration. * Numerous other crash fixes. Once again thanks to all of you for using the Wikipedia iOS app and helping us make it better.. The Wikimedia Reading Team

Hello everyone . We have a fresh release with both visual and “under the hood” improvements. We hope you like it! As always  you can.let us know what you think by leaving a review.. * New App Icon!. * Improved the look of articles by display larger images. . * Removed the progress spinner when loading pages. Instead we now use a less distracting and more informative.progress bar.. * Improved text selection for sharing a fact.. * Improved scrolling performance of the Saved pages list.. * Fixed a bug which caused lead images to be blurry.. * Several fixes to improve the reliability of the history and back button navigation.. * Fixed bug which caused the Hebrew main page to be “collapsed”.. * Improved performance when migrating a large amount of saved articles.. * Fixed crash bug when migrating a large amount of saved articles.. * Several visual bug fixes on the article view.. * Fixed a crash when removing items from history.. * More crash fixes!.

Before we get to what’s new  we have some important information for iOS 6 users: This is our last planned release.which will support iOS 6.. For users who have iOS 6 devices  you can continue use the app for the foreseeable future  but will no longer receive.app updates after 4.1.5. You will also be able to re install 4.1.5 on any of your iOS 6 devices  even if you delete.it.. For users with newer devices  you will be unaffected by this change  except that we have some exciting updates in the.pipeline that were only possible after dropping support for iOS 6.. Now for what’s new:. * Lead images now load faster and fade in smoothly. * Switch article languages quicker with the new button in the.toolbar. * More article layout improvements. * More reliable loading of articles from the cache. * Added a.link to the FAQ in Settings > More. * New translations (Thanks to all our translators!). * Fix crash on.startup for some device languages (Like Norwegian). * Several other crash fixes.
Just a quick release to squash some more bugs!. Release notes:. * Small visual enhancements.  Let us know if you have any issues! Thanks for using the Wikipedia iOS App!.   The Wikimedia Reading Team

Fix several crashes.  Localization updates. Before we go  we want to tell you that we've been busy working another—more exciting—update  and can't wait to share.it with all of you! We're so excited  in fact  that we'd be really happy to have you as beta testers! As a beta tester.you can:.   Get pre release versions of the app before they hit the App Store.  Help us shape the Wikipedia app to better.serve you  the user  by providing crucial feedback.  Have the love and appreciation of all the people working on.the app. If you're interested in helping us with the next (and future) updates  send an email to.mobile ios wikipediawikimedia.org and ask for a beta testing invite. When we publish the beta in a few weeks  you will.receive an email with instructions on how to download the current beta  and once you get set up  you’ll be notified.every time we upload a new beta.. Hope to hear from you soon  and thanks again for using the Wikipedia iOS App!.

This update is focused on improving the stability and experience of the IGN iOS app. We’re recently become aware.of some users experiencing video ads autoplaying in the background while browsing content which is COMPLETELY not our.desire. We’re actively working with Google (the provider of these ads) on finding a way to shut them off and hope to.have this issue resolved ASAP.. Other fixes and changes:. • For folks using the personalized MyFeed feature  duplicate stories in the feed should now no longer be an.issue..    • Sharing content on iPad no longer crashes the app..    • Comment counts on content should now.reflect reality. We still long for a return to our fantasy world  however..    • You can now use native iOS copy /.paste functionality within the app..    • Video pre roll ads can now be paused..    • Numerous bugs squashed.and memory leaks plugged which should reduce the number of crashes. A little over 99% of our sessions are crash free but.that’s still 1% of you that aren’t experiencing the app the way we intended. We’re very sorry for that and will always.endeavor to get as close to 100% uptime as possible.

This should be.transparent to most folks  but ensures the app's ability to continue to run smoothly.

This is a big  juicy update we think you'll love! The headline? Posting is faster  Browsing is richer  and.Yerdling is more social. Post multiple items at once  or store your posts as drafts to finish them later. Search for.fellow Yerdlers and follow their posts by "Liking" them. More in this release:. * Customize your Home screen by picking 3 categories you want to follow  so you.quickly see things you're interested in. We also populate categories based on your previous likes..    *.Re designed Posting flow is super slick: Post multiple items  store drafts. Now you can #HyperYerdle    ready to set a.record for most items posted in a weekend?. * Updated "Me" tab contains all the important sections of your.Yerdle account: Profile  My Wishes  Feedback  Yerdles  Items you've Liked  People you've Liked  Account settings  Invite.friends  Redeem a Promo Code  and Help. * The Shop tab shows you everything on Yerdle. * Search for.people to "Like" them and follow their posts  message them directly. * No more Price Suggestions. *. Wishes Unleashed! Wishes have been one of the most popular ways to shop at Yerdle. So we're going all in. Now.you can make a wish from anything that's ever been given on Yerdle. If we find that item or something like it we'll let.you know. So make sure you turn those notif settings on. And for fairness  if your wish comes true then we'll cross it.off to make room for everyone else. :).   You can now choose to have Yerdle automatically price what you are giving. Figuring out how many dollars a shirt is.worth can be hard. That's why if in 24 hours your item doesn't go then you'll have the  option to let us lower the price.until it finds its new owner. It's the simplest way to declutter and let it go..   Keep an eye out for Free Shipping goodies. If you see the little blue truck it means you won't have to fork over.any real cash to get that item. It's for free for real!.   Easier signup/signin..  Touch ups  polish and wax.. Oh  and if you missed it up there ... you can now see (and wish for!) everything that's ever been given on Yerdle. We.think this is an important step forward on our mission of reuse   giving every thing another life. As of this release.that's 385 221 items and doubling every 3 months.

We thank everyone for their patience and feedback during the time this update was being prepared. We hope you will.enjoy the outcome of the tremendous amount of thought and effort that was put into making this update.. v3.0. .★ Revamped retina user interface.★ Multi tasking enabled. iQuran now efficiently saves and.restores your sessions how you left them..★ Qur'an rendered with a whole new Retina Othmani font.★ Full app is.now 100% landscape enabled. View any view in landscape..★ Super optimized scrolling and landscape switching on all.devices.★ Optimized loading time for translations using complex scripts (Urdu Farsi Bangla Japanese etc). For.example Sura Baqara with Urdu translation now takes ~2sec compared to ~20sec before..★ Many new translations and.updated existing translations (around 14 new translations).★ Tap hold on any verse to see many new options.including a 'Quick Translation' comparison view. In addition to the default translation you can now pick a second.translation to view in this 'Quick View' heads up display .★ Share verses using Email / SMS / Facebook / Twitter or.Copy a verse/translation to paste into any app.★ Revamped Bookmarks and Search interface with collapsible Surah.sections.★ Bookmarks view now includes a Search field to be able to search through bookmarked notes and verses.★ Tap and hold verses in Bookmark and Search view for more options.★ Translation is now visible in Bookmarks and.along with the Arabic text where the user has a translation selected.★ Revamped Index view with a new 'Sections'.view.★ Surah Al Kahf reminders on friday. Switch this ON to be reminder of reading the Surah on every Friday..★ Improved Audio Controls: You can now Pause FF and RW currently played verse..★ You can now select a 'group of.verses' to play during playback (to assist those who wish to memorize the Qur'an). You can now choose to begin playback.from verse 10 and only play the next 5 verses for example. You can then choose to repeat this 'group of verses' using.the existing 'verse repeat' controls..★ A new 'Quranic Supplications' section under 'More'.★ A new helper.section under 'More' explaining the usage of particular 'Stop Signs' encountered while reciting the Holy Qur'an.★.Revamped Surah Info HUD. Tap on the surah name in 'Surah Reading View' to see more information about the chapter such as.its chronological order or alternative name (where applicable)..★ Revamped Bookmark Notes view.★ Copy verses.along with their translation (tap and hold on a verse).★ Floating verse markers in Surah view; you can now see the.currently focused verse number at all times.★ Automatic verse highlighting when verses are scrolled.★ Tons of.optimizations and speed ups; loading all translations (including the previously slow loading translations: urdu bangla.etc).★ Fully localized in Arabic.★ Tons of UI improvements. We're excited to bring you Listen Later  a new feature that lets you save interesting episodes for  you guessed.it  listening to them later. .   Listen Later:  Easily save individual episodes to a Listen Later playlist. Use it when you see something.interesting but don't have time to listen immediately. .   Invite Friends:  We've made it easier to invite your friends to join you on Stitcher   we appreciate your help in.spreading the word!.   iOS7 Compatibility   this version of our app has been tested on iOS7. We've got a big redesign in the works as.well so stay tuned!. IMPORTANT NOTE:  We've changed the behavior of the app to make it easier to explore without interrupting what you're.listening to. Selecting a show now takes you to an info page with more detail and a list of recent episodes. You can.shortcut to just playing the show by tapping the play button at the right edge of the row.

This release addresses a few bugs you've brought to our attention  specifically:.   Fix for problems resuming where you left off in a show in some cases.   Fix for Stitcher starting playback in the background without explicitly asking it to.   Fix for shows not playing fully and skipping to the next show in the playlist.   Fixes for a few crashes experienced by iOS7 listeners.   Improved iOS lock screen integration to display correct progress information. AND FROM OUR PREVIOUS UPDATE:.  .   .  .   .

A better question is what isn’t new?! We’ve taken all your feedback and everything we’ve learned and completely.redesigned the Stitcher app to make it more personalized and simpler to use. Easier to access the shows you love and.discover new ones that you’ll soon love. Let us know what you think at feedbackstitcher.com and check out our blog for.tips & tricks for the new version. Here’s just a bit of the newness:. * MY FRONT PAGE   We’ve reimagined the front page as your personal audio feed. With new episodes from your.favorites  recommendations based on your listening as well as headline news and trending stories  it lets you pop open.Stitcher and instantly start listening to fresh  personalized content. . * SIMPLIFIED NAVIGATION   Access your playlists with a single swipe from anywhere in the app.. * REDESIGNED PLAYER CONTROLS   New Mini Player lets you always see and control what’s playing. Swipe the Mini Player.up to access the full Now Playing view  then swipe down to minimize. You can now access car mode and sleep timer via.the Now Playing screen. . * LAST PLAYED   The new Mini Player automatically loads whatever you were playing last so you can jump right back in .right where you left off.. * MORE PAST EPISODES   New Show Information pages let you access more past episodes than ever before   easily listen .share or save them to your Listen Later playlist.. * RECOMMENDATIONS   Better recommendations  delivered to you on your Front Page as well as on individual Show pages  .for example discover what listeners of This American Life also like to listen to.. * SIMPLIFIED PLAYLISTS   Easier than ever to access  set for offline listening  and manage your favorite shows in.playlists.. * DESIGNED FOR iOS7   Visually refreshed to take advantage of iOS7 design cues and technologically refreshed to.leverage underlying iOS7 technologies.. * SEAMLESS REFRESH   Stitcher seamlessly refreshes and now lets you pull to refresh (swipe down) so you always have.the latest episodes available.. * LISTEN LATER   Easily add episodes from anywhere to your Listen Later playlist   from the Front Page  your.playlists  and past episode lists. Even set it to download for listening to these episodes offline.. * REFRESHED iPAD APP   Oh yeah  a fully updated iPad app as well.

Saavn 4.0 is here  and boy is it an action packed bonanza!. Short version: the whole app is just nicer  with a totally redesigned home screen  more content  better space for My.Music  and much more – you're gonna love it!. Shiny new homepage..One tap access to all areas of the app  including daily New & Trending content  loads.of new Charts  and a Keep Listening section to get back to music you've recently added to your player..   Shiny new My Music  too..Your saved music has a spacious new home. Leave that old cramped apartment behind for.this palatial new space with great light and lots of amenities. Easier player controls..Shuffled (if you'll excuse the pun) the player UI a little bit  so now all your.controls are at the bottom for easy access (even if you have tiny hands).. The long wait is over... new Saavn Pro products are here! You asked for it  you got it: the same great Pro.experience with even more content available  new prices worldwide  and subscriptions for 3 months  6 months  even a.whole year!. Hello  friends. It's a tradition unlike any other... update time! :)  We promised you a big update  and we.weren't kidding. If you're too busy to read the whole spiel  here's a tl;dr haiku:. Player? Redesigned..History? Kept forever..Got FOMO? Read on..      .   Brand New Player.We could give you a song and dance (see what we did there?) about minimalist flat responsive.designy mumbo jumbo  but who cares? It's just way nicer. Your current tracks are front and center  big beautiful album.art  controls tucked away neatly  everything is easier to use  *and* we still kept your queue all in one view so you.don't have to tap around and lose your place... like some *other* music apps we know... cough. How? Magic  that's.how..   Automatic Player History.Worried about losing your queue? Can't find that random song you listened to the.other day? Well fret not! (See  we did it again.) Now we keep track of your full player history  automatically. Cool .right?.   One Tap Playback.We also made playing the content you want even faster. With just one tap on any song  you get.the whole album or playlist  right where you want it. No more duplicates if you play the same thing twice  or crazy .long  unruly player queues. (Unless you want that  in which case you still can   just add to your queue or a playlist.instead right from the....   One Tap Options!.We feel you. Who needs to be diving in and out of song views all the time  just to get some.actions? Aint nobody got time for that! Tap the new options buttons (•••) all around the app  and zappo! Supersonic fast.access to everything you need. Seriously  like laser fast. Pew pew pew!. What's that? Is there more...? YES there is!.   Chromecast Support.You asked for it  you got it. Go ahead  Cast away like Tom Hanks. (To be clear  we don't.know Tom Hanks and he has in no way endorsed this product. I mean he seems very nice  so who knows  he might if we.asked? Or if we wished on the Zoltar machine. But we didn't. He may or may not use Saavn  or Chromecast for that matter..Again  we have no idea. But Castaway was a pretty great movie  right? Willsooooooooon!!! So sad.).   3D Touch Support.Those little application shortcuts were so excited to get out and meet the world last.release  that they snuck out of the house before they we were ready! (Teenagers... what are you gonna do?) Well  if you.have one of those fancy new iPhones with the touchy feely screen  you can now force touch that icon all day errrrrr'day..We put some handy stuff in there for you. Enjoy..   Saavn Pro Gift Cards  Code & More.Where are our Pros at?? Yea  that's you. You can now redeem coupons .gift cards  and special offer codes  right in the app. And by popular demand  if you're not on a recurring subscription. (and if you're not  what are you waiting for? )  you can see how many days of Pro you have left too..   Fixes and Improvements.I mean... not that there were any bugs before. But HYPOTHETICALLY  if there were bugs .we totally wouldn't kill them. That's mean. But we'd  you know  send them on a trip. To  uh  a farm? In Belize.  My Mom's calling.

A bug fix for launch crashes effecting some users on iOS 7. Should be much better now! Plus  all the great stuff.in version 4.3!.  Chromecast fans... our apologies for the frustrating delays. We promise  it's coming very soon!.The app is ready and Chromecast is fully supported  we're just waiting on Google to enable our receiver setup. We'll.make it all live as soon as possible and it won't require an update. Watch Twitter Saavn for updates!.    Version 4.3   .

Hello friends  it's us again. Two more BIG announcements for you in this release!. (Okay  technically three  but one of them is that it's version 5.0 of our app  and you know how excited the product.managers get when they flip over a new version number. You'd think they got a date for the prom or something... it's.just 5.0 this and 5.0 that  all the time around here. We get it already guys  geez  enough with the "high five".jokes.). Alright  on to the parts you really care about..      .   Channels.Finding content just got a whole lot better  with the all new Browse & Discover Channels. Moods.and genres are now beautifully and expertly curated channels  with new and trending content  popular playlists  top.songs  and even quick combo radio stations to get you the exact feel you're looking for.. So whether you're browsing  or not sure what you want  we've got you covered! Heck  even if you're just lazy and.can't pry your potato chip covered body off the couch (get off my back  Mom  am I right? )  you can still find music.you'll love without the hassle of  you know  trying. Just pick what kind of music you want  and it's waiting for you..Oh  and don't forget to follow your favorite channels so we can notify you whenever new content arrives. (It's like.having someone deliver potato chips to you. Who doesn't love takeout? Or potato chips for that matter. Barbecue all the.way!).   Saavn Original Programming  Arriving May 1.Ready for something truly original? Starting May 1  we're.launching a suite of groundbreaking original podcasts and audio programs  only for Saavn listeners! You'll have.exclusive access to incredible long form shows about storytelling  music  sports  journalism  and everything in between..The launch lineup includes:.   Listen to India's favorite radio voice and storyteller  Neelesh Misra  on Qisson ka.Kona..   Hear true crime stories mixed with investigative journalism  starting with the heartbreaking and.controversial Aarushi Files  on Trial by Error..   Hilarious takes on current events from the always irreverent and.inimitable Cyrus Broacha  on Cyrus Says..   Track the hottest new music  hear acoustic sessions  and get insider.interviews from Mae Thomas  on Maed in India. .   And many more!. Yea  we know. What a tease. You have to wait until May 1  when the new shows will automagically premiere on your.homepage. But trust us... it'll be worth the wait!.   Bug Fixes and Improvements.It's really amazing. We keep trying  but we just CAN'T break this darned app. We.try and we try  but we can't create a single bug. Like  what are the chances after all this time? You'd think we'd make.one mistake eventually  right...?? ...cough. Hey  look over ther—  :: runs away ::. But seriously  we fixed lots of stuff. It's way better..   . Until next time  we'll see you dancing in the purple rain.

We're back from TED 2016 in Vancouver! There were some amazing talks by Al Gore  Shonda Rhymes  and Dalia Mogahed.this year that we'd love for you to check out in this fresh release of TED for iOS!. Here's what you'll notice has changed:. * Speaker images should load and cache more reliably..* We heard some folks were having issues viewing popular.talks  so we fixed a bug where the filter button wouldn't appear sometimes as a popover on iPad. Sorry about that! . * We fixed a few weird display bugs that crept in the last release in the iPad video player as well. . * If you.watch a talk that is only available on YouTube  we open it in a Safari view rather than our old  weird embedded YouTube.player. . * You can now quickly access TED's settings via the My Talks tab..* Lots of little UI tweaks here and.there all around the app. Our designer Brian is a stickler for pixel perfection. We do our best to please Brian..

Hey there  TEDsters. We have a few "bug fixes and performance improvements" we wanted to share with you before our.next release..  * We fixed a crash on launch some of you were having after a change on our servers.  . * Loading.the most recent talks should be much faster. You should watch Tim Urban's talk on procrastination. It's great..* We.heard your feedback! The delete button is back on My Talks for the iPad. .

Happy April  TEDsters! We've spent the last few weeks working on improving the stability and reliability of the.app in preparation for some exciting new features and updates we have coming for you over the next few months..  * Fixed an issue with the video player not being full screen in landscape mode..* Talk playback should be more.reliable on poor networks..* Fixed Surprise Me header being cut off on iPhone..* Fixed a potential crasher in.UISearchBar when searching for talks and playlists..* Fixed a few stability and reliability issues around managing.your bookmarks.. We'd love to hear from you. If you run into any issues or have general feedback on our app  email us at.contactted.com..

Hey!. We hope you've been enjoying our recent talks. The Comma Queen  Mary Norris  is our new personal hero.. This month we've got a pretty great release that will make your TED experience much better.. # New Video Player. The biggest change you'll notice is a fresh coat of paint on the TED video player. The video watching experience is.now more seamless on both iPhone and iPad. It also looks much better.. The new video player also lets you rewind a talk you're watching so you can catch every bit of inspiration.. # Universal Links. The TED app now supports universal links. If you tap on a TED.com link from your mailbox  browser or elsewhere on.your phone or tablet  it will automatically open in the app.. # Shave and a haircut. We let our designers take a red pen to the entire app. Line heights were adjusted. Alignments were tweaked.. We'd love to hear from you.

Hi. It's the TED iOS team again. We wanted to push out a few quick fixes for some crashes that were impacting a.subset of users before our next scheduled release. You can find the full 2.7 release notes below.. Talk again soon!. .

Say hello to TED 3.0. We have been hard at work these last few months getting our iOS app localized into twenty.new languages! If you speak Arabic  Chinese (Simplified)  Chinese (Traditional)  Czech  Dutch  French  (pause for.breath)  German  Hebrew  Hungarian  Italian  Japanese  Korean  Polish  Portuguese  Portuguese (Brazilian)  (pause for.breath)  Romanian  Russian  Spanish  Swedish  or (pause for breath)  Turkish you are in for an all new TED experience in.your native language.. Some other changes you'll notice in this release:. * We've highlighted talks in your preferred subtitle language in the Featured tab..* The Featured tab now allows.you to swipe between recent and popular talks..* You can now change your preferred subtitle language in TED.settings..* We've squashed a few smaller bugs and crashes  as we always do.. We'd love to hear from you. If you run into any issues or have general feedback on our app  email us at.contactted.com.. We don't prompt you for a review in the app because we don't want to take away from your time with our speakers..However  if you are enjoying TED for iOS  please take a moment to rate and review us on the App Store. It would mean a.lot to our team!

★ REMEMBER! High ratings keep us motivated to keep adding features  as well as attracting more users and Matches.for you. :).  Emails and profiles are now tagged with location and device information. This means you can now verify the.location (City and Country) of where a user is ACTUALLY emailing you from  not just from where they "say" they are.located in their profile. This helps thwart scammers who say  for example  they live in Los Angeles  CA  but are really.emailing you from some other country. If a user is running this version or later  on every email there will be a new. "From" indicator that tells you the actual location the device was located in when sending the email. If the device is.not capable of sending location information (email was sent from the website or the device had Location Services turned.off for the Dating DNA app)  then it will use the user's IP address to best calculate where they are located. For.example  if it says "From iPhone in: Los Angeles  CA USA" then you can be certain that the email was sent from an iPhone.that was physically in the LA area when the email was sent. If it says "From IP in: Los Angeles  CA USA" then it means.it was sent using an IP address routed via LA. If you want to verify for certain a user's location  tell them to turn on.their Location Services for the DNA app and to email you from within the app. Additionally  this location information.will be displayed in the bottom section of a user's profile  if it's available  so you can view this with Matches .before you even share emails with someone. If you spot a user who has a location listed in their profile which is.drastically different from the verified location information  please flag their profile so we can investigate and remove.them from the system if necessary.. ★ NEW! Big update!.   Pick grains from an included list. Points and lovibond are automatically included.   Estimate final beer color (SRM).   Use as many grains as you like  no longer limited to 6.  Alpha acid is automatically included..   Bitterness (IBU) is calculated based on hop boil time.   Using built in UI widgets to manage tables and pickers.   Image updates.   Got rid of many sounds (started to annoy me after awhile  they may come back in the next version).   Several UI tweaks for better consistency.   Fixed a few bugs and typos.         . UP NEXT:.   Yeast selection.Select yeast from a list... including yeast attenuation and fermentation temperatures..   Settings tab.Change all of the defaults from a central settings tab..   Styles tab.Brew Pal will try to match a BJCP style to what you are brewing based on your grain bill  and offer.suggestions..   Other additions.Fruit  honey  pepper  etc..   Save/Load/Export.Once you enter a complete recipe into Brew Pal  save it for later reference or email it to.yourself.. ...they might not all happen in the next update  but they are all on my to do list.

Load/Save/Export. The #1 requested feature! Now you can save and browse your recipes  as well as email.them to yourself.   BJCP Styles. Compare your brew to BJCP style guidelines.   Yeast selection.    Settings. Manage all settings from one settings tab.   Scale your recipe. Optionally scale your ingredients when you change the batch size.   Bug fixes. No longer crashes with very low SRM values. Calculate original gravity based on grain.bill correctly (was off by about 10% previously). Allow for batch sizes and grain weights > 99.     .    Other additions. Fruit  honey  pepper  flavorings  etc..   Carbonation. Keg carbonation calculator.   SRM swatch. Compare your brew to a visual list of colors.   Flavor wheel. Narrow in on that taste or smell.   Notes. Save notes along with your recipe

Yeast selector display bug fixed

Dry hopping. Add hops to your fermenter.   Additions. Add finings and flavorings to your boil or fermenter.   Timers (with alarm). Countdown timers track your mash  boil  and fermentation.         . Enhancements:.   0 minute hops and additions are now allowed.   Live recipe editing... no need to re save.   Better formatted export with much more information.

Improved hop AA selection.   Muted timer ticking sound by default.   UI tweaks  bug fixes  stability improvements

Settings for batch  fly  infusion or decoction mashing and sparging  including mashout.   Ability to set a constant sparge water temperature.   Added "trub loss" settings for boil and fermentation. Batch sizes over 999 gal/L are allowed.   Live editing of recipes is remembered when Brew Pal is relaunched.   New "Lager" setting in the Yeast tab to double the pitching rate.   Boil time and fermentation time can be set in the Timers tab independently of the Settings.   As always  interface tweaks and bug fixes. A "planned debt free date" now displays  on the Debts screen as an estimate of when all of the debts listed will.be repaid. This date will change based on what is input in the Additional Amount field in Configure Snowball..   The amount in Configure Snowball is now taken into account when figuring out the estimated time remaining for the.first debt in the list (and for estimating the planned debt free date)..   The amount in Configure Snowball now applies to the next debt in line if there is money left over that month from.Configure Snowball after the previous debt was repaid..   The "estimated time left" for each debt has been added to the Debts screen  so that you can easily see what effect.just paying the minimums on the other individual debts will have..   Fixed a few bugs  including one where the the estimated time left for debts with 0% interest could not be.calculated..   Improved overall application stability.

Ability to password protect the app if desired..   Ability to change the password to something else or to turn the password off if it has been set..   Ability to turn off the snowball if you'd like to see how much time it would take to pay off each debt by just.paying minimum payments..   Modified the way estimated time left is calculated for each debt in the list so that it takes into account the.effects of the snowball. As part of this change  12 months is now used by default as the number of payment periods per.year. If you are updating from a previous version  under certain circumstances this change may also adjust the planned.debt free date to make it more accurate.
